{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/506"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–506","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1972-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1972","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/86/907"},"text":"86 Stat. 907","children":[],"tail":", which is not classified to the Code."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Vocational Education Act of 1963, referred to in par. (10), was title I of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/210"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–210","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1963-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 1963","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/77/403"},"text":"77 Stat. 403","children":[],"tail":", as amended generally by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/482/tII/s202/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–482, title II, § 202(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/2169"},"text":"90 Stat. 2169","children":[],"tail":", which was classified to chapter 44 (§ 2301 et seq.) of this title, prior to amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/524/s1"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–524, § 1","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-19"},"text":"Oct. 19, 1984","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/98/2435"},"text":"98 Stat. 2435","children":[],"tail":", striking out all after the enacting clause and inserting in lieu thereof titles I to V, to be cited as the Carl D. Perkins Vocational Education Act. The Act was subsequently amended extensively by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/392"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–392","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-09-25"},"text":"Sept. 25, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/753"},"text":"104 Stat. 753","children":[],"tail":", which renamed it